ht.)  However, my friend on the Plane of Firiona Vie is a half elf.  Although a weaker race, he is a good sort and stout of heart.  If you see him, think on him as a friend.  His name is Vanstorm, and he is a troubled youth, for his father, a close friend, was recently lost at sea.<br>
